git checkout trunk
vi ChangeLog
vi rmol.spec
\endverbatim

Commit the change-logs and publish the trunk (main development branch):
\verbatim
git commit -m "[Doc] Integrated the change-log of the release 0.50.0."
git push
\endverbatim
